! Namespace — settings & diagnostics

Read-only view of what the resolver currently sees: pseudo-segments,
aliases, mount points, and the backlinks index. Click through to the
defining tiddler for each.

!! Pseudo-segments

Modules registered as `module-type: rimir-ns-pseudo`. Each handles
one `_foo` token encountered as a path segment.

<$list filter="[all[tiddlers+shadows]is[system]prefix[$:/plugins/]] :filter[<currentTiddler>has[module-type]get[module-type]match[rimir-ns-pseudo]]" emptyMessage="<em>none registered</em>">
* <$link to=<<currentTiddler>>/> — <code>{{{ [<currentTiddler>get[title]] }}}</code>
</$list>

!! Exact aliases

