!! Mount points

Tiddlers tagged `$:/tags/NamespaceMount` with `from` + `to`.

<$list filter="[all[tiddlers+shadows]tag[$:/tags/NamespaceMount]]" emptyMessage="<em>none defined</em>">
* <code><$view field="from"/></code> → <code><$view field="to"/></code> &nbsp;<span style="opacity:0.7;">(<$link to=<<currentTiddler>>>source</$link>)</span>
</$list>

!! Diagnostic filters

These operators are exposed for scripting / debugging:

* `[<ref>ns-resolve<source>]` — resolve a single ref as if from `<source>`
* `[<ref>ns-resolve-class<source>]` — CSS class (`ns-resolved` / `ns-unresolved`)
* `[<title>ns-backlinks[]]` — sources that reference `<title>`
* `[<title>ns-forwardlinks[]]` — targets `<title>` references

Tiddler info sidebar includes a ''NS Backlinks'' tab showing the reverse
index for the current tiddler.
